*Hoćemo* da vidimo šta će se dogoditi (We want to see what will happen)

*Hoćeš* li da pomogneš? (Will you help?)

Svi *hoćemo* da se zaštitimo (We all want to protect ourselves)

Ona *hoće* da nastavi svoju potragu (She wants to continue her search)

*Hoćemo* li da se vratimo ranije? (Should we go back earlier?)

Oni *hoće* da podignu nivo obrazovanja (They want to raise the level of education)

*Hoću* da znam šta je sljedeće na redu (I want to know what's next on the agenda)

*Hoćemo* li da pričamo o tome? (Should we talk about it?)